WEBVTT

00:00:00.080 --> 00:00:15.598
All right, good morning family. I have an urgency in my spirit right now to pray, so I’m just going to jump right into it and intercede. There are some things happening and I have an alert.

00:00:15.599 --> 00:00:25.674
When I get these, I’m just letting you all come in with me to pray over the election in Pennsylvania right now and the corruption I've seen.

00:00:25.675 --> 00:00:33.886
Diana, you can just jump right in. I’m going to pray in the spirit as I pray.

00:00:33.887 --> 00:00:36.194
If you may not understand it, it’s the baptism of the Holy Spirit.

00:00:36.195 --> 00:02:50.598
I don’t have time to explain it today, but we’ll have more time later.

00:02:50.599 --> 00:03:01.594
Holy Spirit, we flow for what you have for us now. We yield ourselves to you.

00:03:01.595 --> 00:03:08.111
Father, we thank you. We're not moved by emotion; we're moved by what the spirit says.

00:03:08.112 --> 00:03:21.901
Filled with and controlled by the Holy Ghost now, pray through us even more, Holy Spirit, as we yield ourselves to move.

00:03:21.902 --> 00:03:25.263
We pray for the hidden things. We come in boldly and we pray for the hidden things.

00:03:25.264 --> 00:05:32.603
In the stillness of the night, we uncover those things by angelic manifestation right now.

00:05:32.604 --> 00:05:44.345
In the stillness of the night, we uncover those things. We see the trucks; we see the ballots.

00:05:44.346 --> 00:06:03.872
I see you in the spirit and I uncover you in the name of Jesus. We send the angels now in Jesus'name for manifestation of this war and the corruption.

00:06:03.873 --> 00:06:40.739
We call for the corruption to be found out in Jesus'name. Pennsylvania, you will not do this, nor Virginia.

00:06:40.740 --> 00:07:05.171
We rise up in prayer. We take it. As they make their move, we thank you, Lord, that the plans of the enemy are foiled.

00:07:05.172 --> 00:07:22.797
It's not enough; they underestimated. Their plans are of the wicked and their minds are reprobate.

00:07:22.798 --> 00:07:36.804
We call forth the mind to be healed over the reprobate mind. We pray over it, Father, right now in the name of Jesus.

00:07:36.805 --> 00:07:45.990
This demonic thinking, we bind that, Father, for you said we wrestle not against flesh and blood, but against principalities, powers, and spiritual wickedness in high places.

00:07:45.991 --> 00:08:11.253
Father, we take authority over those devils right now in the name of Jesus, over that reprobate mind.

00:08:11.254 --> 00:08:46.766
We render you completely helpless now. We're going to Texas now.

00:08:46.767 --> 00:10:00.999
We're in Houston, for it will be decided in Houston, Lord, by each county. over Cruz, we pray over you in the name of Jesus.

00:10:01.000 --> 00:10:12.505
Over Austin, Texas; over Austin, you've gone predominantly liberal and we will not have this.

00:10:12.506 --> 00:11:38.119
We turn it now. Over Dallas, Fort Worth, and Arlington; over Helotes, San Antonio.

00:11:38.120 --> 00:11:58.710
Jesus, we're not moved by what we see or what we feel; we're moved by what the word says, and we have the victory in the name of Jesus.

00:11:58.711 --> 00:12:46.185
Now we're going to Atlanta, Georgia. We take authority over the spirit of racism in Jesus'name.

00:12:46.186 --> 00:13:00.680
We bind that spirit. You're a foul stench; get out of here in the name of Jesus.

00:13:00.681 --> 00:13:11.679
Racism will not do this. Father, we thank you for a mending of the hearts.

00:13:11.680 --> 00:13:18.850
There's great hurt in the hearts from generation to generation.

00:13:18.851 --> 00:13:50.137
We minister to the African-Americans in the spirit. We pray peace and call comfort over their hearts.

00:13:50.138 --> 00:14:18.157
We call for peace and restoration. Everything that was stolen, Father, for the cankerworm has been found.

00:14:18.158 --> 00:14:23.398
We call out that cankerworm and say restoration of double in Jesus'name.

00:14:23.399 --> 00:14:52.807
Restoration of double in the name of Jesus to make things right.

00:14:52.808 --> 00:17:55.239
This will happen in the spirit. The hearts in the Deep South; the roots of heart to be heard. Is anyone listening to me? All the way through Chicago.

00:17:55.240 --> 00:18:16.002
Father, only you can fix this, Lord, by your grace, your mercy, the anointing, and the glory.

00:18:16.003 --> 00:18:49.192
The glory breaks down the walls of pain, hurt, and bitterness. A wave of glory on this nation from coast to coast.

00:18:49.193 --> 00:19:06.606
I call for a restoration over the Hispanic community, the Latinos. Father, we pray for a revival over the Hispanic community.

00:19:06.607 --> 00:19:27.126
Father, we call forth the fire of God to visit their churches and the people.

00:19:27.127 --> 00:19:48.512
Over the Cubans, over the Puerto Ricans, we call forth a supernatural visitation and manifestation of the glory.

00:19:48.513 --> 00:20:10.449
They have been lied to by so many. I thank you, Father, for great discernment, not just hearing what we want to hear, but hearing what you say.

00:20:10.450 --> 00:21:17.208
We're not being lied to by the enemy. Lord, you're showing me so much. We speak for the Senate to be red.

00:21:17.209 --> 00:21:40.376
The embarrassment that they do not want to face, they are trying to cover up out of corruption. It's in these certain counties.

00:21:40.377 --> 00:22:47.523
I'm looking at individual corruption in the counties, swaying certain counties to go blue, trying to control the vote by a margin, a thin line of maybe 20,000 votes placed in strategic places so it's not detectable.

00:22:47.524 --> 00:23:08.685
Father, let all hidden things be revealed. We wake up the Boomers in every culture, tribe, and tongue.

00:23:08.686 --> 00:24:03.578
We wake up the Boomers, the elderly generation, for they will carry this one more time.

00:24:03.579 --> 00:24:21.722
Lord said, 'I only need one more time,'for there will be a beginning of a quick work.

00:24:21.723 --> 00:24:57.947
The manifestations of my glory will come in a wave you've never seen before—a great red wave.

00:24:57.948 --> 00:25:14.827
They underestimated it, for they have a reprobate mind. They are not thinking with the mind of Christ; they think with a demonic mind.

00:25:14.828 --> 00:25:30.923
Their math is off. There's a spirit of confusion in their camp and it rests heavily on them.

00:25:30.924 --> 00:25:43.254
As they do corruption, the spirit of confusion is heavy in the camp—bickering and strife among them.

00:25:43.255 --> 00:26:23.768
Where there is strife, there is confusion and every evil work. It's infiltrating their camps right now.

00:26:23.769 --> 00:26:43.484
The enemy is not the people; they have yielded themselves over to a demonic spirit.

00:26:43.485 --> 00:27:11.839
You're not wrestling against people; this is an antichrist spirit opposing my word.

00:27:11.840 --> 00:27:24.161
We're praying for their salvation and that the blinders Satan has placed over the eyes of the unbeliever be taken off.

00:27:24.162 --> 00:28:01.599
We pray for unity and peace, and that they would see the errors in their ways. It's not blue against red; it's light against darkness.

00:28:01.600 --> 00:28:22.897
We call for their eyes to be enlightened, even tomorrow in the polling booth.

00:28:22.898 --> 00:28:44.319
Angels of the Lord, manifest and make war against those demonic spirits right now.

00:28:44.320 --> 00:29:24.490
Father, we thank you that even the counties in California are fed up. I see it.

00:29:24.491 --> 00:29:46.908
Even the ones that would want to sway to the far left are fed up with the taxes and the unfair treatment.

00:29:46.909 --> 00:30:00.959
I see even great Hollywood celebrities saying they're frustrated with the way this is going with Gavin Newsom.

00:30:00.960 --> 00:30:12.479
I call a red wave in Jesus'name, a turnout of red like they've never seen before, because they want hope and change.

00:30:12.480 --> 00:30:40.589
But the only one that will bring great change is you, through preaching righteousness and holiness, not a seeker-friendly gospel. Break the chains, Father.

00:30:40.590 --> 00:31:49.912
As we go into Nevada and Arizona, we pray for Kari Lake and the others, that they come out bolder and stronger with a backbone like a crowbar.

00:31:49.913 --> 00:32:13.946
We send angels in the nighttime when corruption tries to be at its greatest. We call for an uncovering and exposing of things.

00:32:13.947 --> 00:32:57.779
We call for uncorrupt police to show up and have the boldness to expose it, to abide by their oath and the stirring of a conscience inside of them to blow the whistle in the darkness.

00:32:57.780 --> 00:33:06.397
We pray for the postal workers; if there is corruption, let them be found out.

00:33:06.398 --> 00:33:24.117
If they try to bury or burn the ballots, let them be found in Jesus'name.

00:33:24.118 --> 00:34:47.277
You've shown me the corruption in these people, Father, but we call these things around right now. I saw the truck, and it was like an unmarked truck.

00:34:47.278 --> 00:34:58.319
But the Lord was saying to me, 'They undershot.'They were trying to be sneaky, but they undershot.

00:34:58.320 --> 00:35:48.559
They don't have enough time. Especially in that county—it’s Pennsylvania. I saw the number 23,000.

00:35:48.560 --> 00:36:03.495
Father, we take communion and thank you that all hidden things will be revealed.

00:36:03.496 --> 00:36:26.576
We see the red wave starting in Michigan, Minnesota, Illinois.

00:36:26.577 --> 00:37:03.140
I pray for a red wave in Jesus'name, an uncontainable wave of glory upon this land from sea to shining sea.

00:37:03.141 --> 00:37:53.096
I saw in the spirit a dark storm upon the East Coast. Out of this, I saw four beautiful white doves circling in figure-eights.

00:37:53.097 --> 00:38:13.649
The glory of the Lord was resting on four doves. It either means four years or four consecutive years.

00:38:13.650 --> 00:38:33.869
The storm was violent, but there was light in Goshen. I saw the house again, with the place being prepared.

00:38:33.870 --> 00:38:58.503
Psalms 91 and Psalms 23. He prepares a table before me in the presence of my enemies.

00:38:58.504 --> 00:39:15.697
Surely goodness and mercy follow us all the days of our life.

00:39:15.698 --> 00:39:35.918
We stand in the gap for America. Father, you have a great plan for America.

00:39:35.919 --> 00:39:45.716
One last push. A four-year window here before Jesus Christ comes.

00:39:45.717 --> 00:40:15.287
We need a revival beyond anything we can comprehend. I feel the presence of the Lord.

00:40:15.288 --> 00:40:48.974
Holy Spirit, invade these people in their homes. Father, you have one last call for America.

00:40:48.975 --> 00:41:15.118
We pray for your hand of judgment to be upon the wicked. Remove those that stand in the way of your great revival.

00:41:15.119 --> 00:41:50.572
One last call for a harvest. Four years. The Holy Spirit represents the glory that descended on Jesus like a dove.

00:41:50.573 --> 00:42:26.293
We invite you. Four years. You give America four more years for a supernatural harvest.

00:42:26.294 --> 00:44:03.279
I saw those doves go into solid light; they became one big light and it dispatched over all the glory.

00:44:03.280 --> 00:45:00.759
It's spreading over Texas, over Houston. The glory of the latter house will be greater than the former.

00:45:00.760 --> 00:46:39.488
Four years of the greater glory. This is what you've prayed for. It started from Rosh Hashanah to Rosh Hashanah.

00:46:39.489 --> 00:47:11.263
First the blade, then the ear, then the full manifestation of the glory.

00:47:11.264 --> 00:47:37.877
This is your window. What will you do with the time I've given you?

00:47:37.878 --> 00:48:10.256
For my son's return is imminent. The sun is setting on this dispensation. It's time for you to soar.

00:48:10.257 --> 00:48:32.394
I saw the glory of the Lord flowing in each individual person as they come up higher to the throne.

00:48:32.395 --> 00:49:08.410
There's a special place prepared for each of you. It's by grace. It's a renewing of your mind.

00:49:08.411 --> 00:49:28.959
Change the way you think because it's been in reprobate thinking.

00:49:28.960 --> 00:49:47.201
You allowed the enemy to tell you that you're not good enough, but I've done it all.

00:49:47.202 --> 00:50:38.098
I see everyone sitting before the throne, resting. So you've got to take your place.

00:50:38.099 --> 00:51:23.187
He's coming soon. I'm going to give you one last call. Will you squander this time or will you march on and take the land with me?

00:51:23.188 --> 00:51:37.566
For the harvest is plentiful and the laborers are few. Who will help me bring in my harvest?

00:51:37.567 --> 00:52:17.786
These are no longer last days; I'm giving you seconds. I am right at the door.

00:52:17.787 --> 00:52:39.988
It's time for you all to come up higher. Take the care out of the prayer and shake off the beggar's cloak.

00:52:39.989 --> 00:53:11.658
Like blind Bartimaeus had to throw off the beggar's cloak. In the spirit, you have to take off the old leper's cloak and come up higher.

00:53:11.659 --> 00:54:25.277
How do you see yourself? Bound and broken, or seated with me in the heavenlies?

00:54:25.278 --> 00:54:59.463
You can pluck like chickens or soar like eagles. You choose by renewing your mind and staying in prayer.

00:54:59.464 --> 00:56:54.076
I am standing at the door. He's coming through the door. It's no longer days; it's seconds.

00:56:54.077 --> 00:57:49.946
He's given us a window. I extended the grace. I've given you a little window, a fraction, and the glorious church will rise out of it.

00:57:49.947 --> 00:58:01.833
It's about the next Shemitah cycle. If you don't know what the Shemitah is, go read Rabbi Jonathan Cahn's book on the Shemitah.

00:58:01.834 --> 00:58:32.063
When the next Shemitah cycle ends in 2028, this is a great window.

00:58:32.064 --> 00:58:47.722
What will you do with that timeframe? It has everything to do with the Shemitah cycle.

00:58:47.723 --> 00:59:05.955
Father, we thank you for your body that was broken for us. We dedicate our lives to come up higher and shake off the beggar's cloak.

00:59:05.956 --> 00:59:28.879
We are sons and daughters of the Most High God. We will walk in victory and light.

00:59:28.880 --> 00:59:39.089
Let that light shine through us today. Father, we thank you for the blood.

00:59:39.090 --> 01:00:42.476
I thank you, Lord, that our eyes are being flooded with light.

01:00:42.477 --> 01:01:04.123
We plead the blood over America, Asia, Africa, Russia, and South America.

01:01:04.124 --> 01:02:22.187
It's time. I saw all God's children sitting by his throne. All different cultures, no race, no color.

01:02:22.188 --> 01:03:08.974
He doesn't see through the eyes of stupidity; he sees everyone as one.

01:03:08.975 --> 01:04:00.447
The devil has tried so hard to blind people with race, gender, and age.

01:04:00.448 --> 01:04:44.641
What will we do before the next Shemitah cycle in 2028? He's coming quick.

01:04:44.642 --> 01:05:14.672
If you haven't asked him into your heart, there are no more delays.

01:05:14.673 --> 01:05:56.985
Say a simple prayer: 'Father, forgive me of my sins. Write my name in the Lamb's Book of Life.

01:05:56.986 --> 01:06:12.846
I believe you're the Son of God.'Get baptized, find a church, stop sinning, and get in the Word every day.

01:06:12.847 --> 01:06:53.963
You have the Great Commission to lay hands on the sick, cast out devils, and raise the dead.

01:06:53.964 --> 01:07:14.804
Do something big before the next Shemitah cycle. I'm going to keep doing these prayer videos.

01:07:14.805 --> 01:07:59.589
We're going to have good results in Jesus'name. We plowed like an icebreaker today.

01:07:59.590 --> 01:09:36.608
I'm never in a hurry when the presence is thick. Why worry about things that don't count for eternity?

01:09:36.609 --> 01:09:51.475
Everything's about eternity. Some people focusing on earthly things will realize how foolish they were.

01:09:51.476 --> 01:11:48.325
I don't talk about the Thousand Years because I don't have scripture to back up the specific things I've seen, but it's beautiful.

01:11:48.326 --> 01:12:13.789
Everything's restored. No smog, no pollution. Vegetables the size of beachballs.

01:12:13.790 --> 01:13:49.035
We'll be in a glorified body. I'm taking these doTERRA peppermint beads.

01:13:49.036 --> 01:15:00.097
They help a lot. I was focusing on those doves. The glory went out as they spread over the earth.

01:15:00.098 --> 01:15:32.861
I saw a fire going around the middle of the earth. The Holy Spirit fire spreading glory around the whole earth.

01:15:32.862 --> 01:16:38.680
I believe each dove represents four years. Jesus is standing at the door.

01:16:38.681 --> 01:18:53.362
What will you do with that window? Subscribe and like the video. We will pray again tomorrow.

01:18:53.363 --> 01:19:16.461
We're believing this thing is over today and will be called quickly in Jesus'name. God bless you all.

